init_text:
A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She’s unaware that she’s actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who’s fallen for her, and is certain he’s going to get it right this time.

One day,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He decided to take her to a restaurant that he knew she loved.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He picked her up in his car, and they drove to the restaurant.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: He was going to make this the best date ever.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: When they arrived, he opened the door for her, and they walked into the restaurant.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The waiter took their drink orders, and they looked over the menu.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The shapeshifter had been to this restaurant many times, so he knew exactly what to order.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The waiter came back with their drinks, and they ordered their meals.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: The waiter brought their food, and they began to eat.
